reviewText: IT DID ARRIVE QUICKLY. BUT WHEN I WATCHED IT TODAY, IT WAS ONLY 16 MINUTES LONG. IT DIDN'T SAY HOW LONG IT WAS IN THE DESCRIPTION. THAT'S INCLUDING THE MINUTE OR SO INTRODUCTION AT THE BEGINNING AND 2 COMMERCIALS AT THE END. IT WAS A VERY CUTE VIDEO FOR WHAT IT WAS, BUT WAS DEFINETELY NOT WORTH IT.
